    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> Use the <parameter>multi-line-suffix()</parameter> option when processing multi-line messages. Specify a string or regular expression that matches the end of the multi-line message.</para>
    <para>To use the <parameter>multi-line-suffix()</parameter> option, set the <parameter>multi-line-mode()</parameter> option to <userinput>prefix-suffix</userinput>. See also the <parameter>multi-line-prefix()</parameter> option.</para>
